WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.760
Barclays Online Banking

2
00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:03.720
How to register

3
00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:12.320
to register for Online Banking,
start by clicking on ‘Register’.

4
00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:17.280
Next, scroll down, and read
the important information carefully.

5
00:00:18.680 --> 00:00:20.200
Then, click ‘Start’.

6
00:00:21.040 --> 00:00:24.040
Type in your surname
as it appears on your account,

7
00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:25.960
your date of birth,

8
00:00:26.360 --> 00:00:27.440
your postcode

9
00:00:28.840 --> 00:00:30.720
and your Email address twice.

10
00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:41.200
Select this box if you do not want Barclays
to contact you about products or services.

11
00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:44.200
Then select the type of account you have,

12
00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:46.640
enter the details

13
00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:50.680
and then click ‘Next’.

14
00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:55.040
If you haven't previously registered
for Online Banking,

15
00:00:55.480 --> 00:00:57.720
you'll be taken to a confirmation screen

16
00:00:57.720 --> 00:01:01.120
where you can scroll down to check
your details are correct.

17
00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:04.560
If you're happy,
click on ‘Confirm’.

18
00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:05.920
And that's it,

19
00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:08.640
you're now registered for Online Banking.

20
00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:12.520
You'll be able to log in as soon as you
receive your passcode,

21
00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:17.280
which should arrive at your home
address within 5 working days.

22
00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:19.920
Scroll down and if you wish,

23
00:01:20.160 --> 00:01:23.880
you can select this box so your membership
number is remembered,

24
00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:27.800
which will speed up logging
into Online Banking in the future.

25
00:01:32.920 --> 00:01:35.240
And there you are, you’re all set up.

26
00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:41.000
You can now click ‘Back to Homepage’
to return to the Barclays homepage.

